Package stork.ad Description

Contains the classes for the Ad library, a marshalling library developed for Stork. It converts between Java objects and JSON (as well as other data representation formats). Its name comes from its historical purpose as a ClassAd parser implementation. Though the ClassAd format was dropped in favor of using JSON for communication, ClassAd parsing and rendering is still supported.
